{"data":[{"date":"14:25 16/06","title":"Juan Mata v\u00e0 Fabregas c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn David de Gea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/juan-mata-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-david-de-gea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juan Mata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 tin r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 28 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, De Gea s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mata tin De Gea s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 gi\u1eefa T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David de Gea \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Ph\u00fat 44, t\u1eeb c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, De Gea l\u1ea1i b\u1eaft tr\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u00f3ng bi\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng cho B\u0110N m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juan Mata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea sau sai l\u1ea7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u0110N h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juan Mata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea sau sai l\u1ea7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u0110N h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/juan-mata-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-david-de-gea.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mata tin De Gea s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nRonaldo th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m r\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0 c\u1ee7a De Gea, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a De Gea tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn anh g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nKh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng HLV TBN n\u00ean c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 De Gea ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, b\u1edfi d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nJuan Mata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 tin r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 28 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, De Gea s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng\u00a0ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, th\u1eddi gian s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng De Gea s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eeda sai\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fabregas c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o De Gea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia cho BBC, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ces Fabregas n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a De Gea.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN De Gea mac sai lam\" title=\"TBN De Gea mac sai lam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-sai-lam-cua-david-de-gea.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabregas kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n De Gea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a De Gea nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i th\u00eam, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i v\u00e0 NHM T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nRio Ferdinand th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh De Gea, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng De Gea s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-sai-lam-cua-david-de-gea-421-188619.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mourinho th\u00ec chia s\u1ebb</span>: \u201cNh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap De Gea tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"231","checkdouble":"188632"},{"date":"14:46 16/06","title":"Chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Alisson s\u1eafp k\u00fd v\u1edbi Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/chi-tiet-hop-dong-alisson-sap-ky-voi-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gianluca Di Marzio \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, song n\u0103m nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i, Los Blancos mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Real-Madrid-mua-Alisson-thanh-cong-voi-gia-52-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Real s\u1ebd mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Courtois hay David de Gea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u0111\u01b0a tin, De Gea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi MU, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c Real ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia, anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoma kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nho-thuyet-khach-liverpool-sap-co-thu-mon-moi-172-187344.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alisson</span>. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Real Madrid v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9\u00a0th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gianluca Di Marzio cung c\u1ea5p. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Real-Madrid-mua-Alisson-thanh-cong-voi-gia-52-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Alisson\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Alisson, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, t\u1ea1i Bernabeu Alisson s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 250.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng Real s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018, song v\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, Real ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong khi Roma \u0111\u00f2i 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ee7 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"230","checkdouble":"188633"},{"date":"14:06 16/06","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Argentina vs Iceland: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 20h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 16/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Argentina vs Iceland: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 20h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 16/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d-463-188637.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ARGENTINA VS ICELAND</strong></u></span></span><br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"229","checkdouble":"188634"},{"date":"14:18 16/06","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u2018h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u2019 c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/them-mot-cau-thu-hang-thai-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-chinh-thuc-co-ben-do-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, BL\u0110 CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/8/tien-ve-Hoang-Van-Binh-cua-FLC-Thanh-Hoa-chinh-thuc-co-ben-do-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB SLNA</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n thanh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. Sau khi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n hai v\u00e0 anh nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng SLNA.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec h\u00f4m qua (15/6), \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sinh n\u0103m 1989 t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef3nh L\u01b0u, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a v\u1edbi Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, \u00c2u V\u0103n Ho\u00e0n,\u2026 - nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 SLNA t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2007... B\u1eb1ng n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T U20 Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m 2011, Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 SEA Games. C\u0169ng trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf SLNA, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng C\u00fap c\u00f9ng CLB (V.League 2011, C\u00fap QG 2010 v\u00e0 si\u00eau c\u00fap 2011).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a SLNA trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a V\u0103n B\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-188634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-188634.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Th\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\">Sao HAGL ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a VFF</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c CLB sau v\u00f2ng 13 V-League, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn sau h\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00a0Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"228","checkdouble":"188635"},{"date":"14:30 16/06","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo D\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang n\u1eafm t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Tien-dao-Van-Quyet-nhan-dinh-du-doan-tran-Argentina-vs-Iceland-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m trong tay Argentina</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi C.Ronaldo c\u00f3 m\u00e0n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam qua, th\u00ec v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 16/6, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Messi c\u0169ng s\u1ebd x\u1ecf gi\u00e0y ra s\u00e2n tham gia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Argentina vs Iceland.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Messi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Messi v\u00e0 Argentina s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;&ldquo;World Cup 2014 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Messi c\u00f9ng Argentina khi thua \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c, Ph\u00e1p&nbsp;nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i v\u1eabn tin \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 31, M10 s\u1ebd ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i trong k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Argentina l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Iceland kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t, ch\u1edd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 &quot;nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng&quot; c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Gylfi Sigurdsson - c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Everton t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i Euro 2016, Iceland t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi t\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Argentina c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&rdquo;, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d-463-188637.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d-463-188637.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Argentina vs Iceland 20h00 ng\u00e0y 16/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Argentina vs Iceland: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2014. Anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;Argentina nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi Iceland v\u1ed1n l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. N\u1ebfu t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed v\u00e0 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t,&nbsp;t\u00f4i tin Argentina s\u1ebd th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 Messi s\u1ebd l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa <span href=\"Argentina vs Iceland\" target=\"_blank\">Argentina vs Iceland</span> s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 20h00 t\u1ed1i nay tr\u00ean VTV6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-argentina-vs-iceland-20h00-ngay-166-giai-ma-hien-tuong-421-188591.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-argentina-vs-iceland-20h00-ngay-166-giai-ma-hien-tuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-argentina-vs-iceland-20h00-ngay-166-giai-ma-hien-tuong-421-188591.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Iceland (20h00 ng\u00e0y 16/6): Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean Leo Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Iceland b\u1ea3ng D World Cup...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"227","checkdouble":"188636"},{"date":"14:32 16/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Argentina vs Iceland 20h00 ng\u00e0y 16/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Argentina vs Iceland: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 20h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 16/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Argentina vs Iceland: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 20h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 16/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d-463-188637.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ARGENTINA VS ICELAND</strong></u></span></span><br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"226","checkdouble":"188637"},{"date":"14:54 16/06","title":"HLV Riedl n\u00f3i ph\u0169 v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-riedl-noi-phu-ve-giac-mo-world-cup-cua-bong-da-viet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00ean l\u1ec1 VCK World Cup 2018, c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00f4ng Alfred Riedl \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 suy ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>HLV Riedl: B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 World Cup n\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y!</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i U19 v\u00e0 U23 \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i VCK ch\u00e2u \u00c1, trong \u0111\u00f3 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Riedl n\u00f3i ph\u0169 v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Riedl n\u00f3i ph\u0169 v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/1-1529073604-width500height333.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Riedl kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a HLV Riedl th\u00ec ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u01b0\u1edfng ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, khi m\u00e0 su\u1ed1t 10 n\u0103m qua, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf \u0110TQG Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd Zing.vn, \u00f4ng Riedl \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 trong h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m qua. G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn n\u00e0o gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2007 v\u00e0 n\u0103m 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb khu v\u1ef1c. Sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c World Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho vi\u1ec7c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t bao l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi C\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u01b0? \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n trong ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Riedl ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c khi m\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111ang loay hoay t\u00ecm l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t cho b\u00e0i to\u00e1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 10 n\u0103m qua ch\u00fang ta lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 chung tay c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00ean th\u00ec gi\u1ea5c m\u1ed9ng World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi s\u1ed1 su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2026.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"225","checkdouble":"188640"},{"date":"15:07 16/06","title":"S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 11: Nh\u1eadt k\u00fd World Cup ng\u00e0y 15/6","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-11-nhat-ky-world-cup-ngay-156.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00e0y 15/6 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u World Cup b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u gu\u1ed3ng quay trung b\u00ecnh 3 tr\u1eadn/ ng\u00e0y. S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 11 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n t\u1edbi v\u1edbi d\u01b0 \u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra bao g\u1ed3m derby Iberia gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</h2><br>\r\n<strong>Clip S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 11:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OyYTh_jjSUU\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> </strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y 15/6 nh\u00ecn chung di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i gi\u1ed1ng nhau. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t, Uruguay t\u1ea1o ra th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ai C\u1eadp nh\u01b0ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 90, Jose Gimenez v\u1edbi pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh m\u1edbi mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 cho Uruguay. C\u0169ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 Iran v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi mu\u1ed9n h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. Ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 5, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Aziz Bouhaddouz \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi \u201cngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c\u201d gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ea1 Ma-r\u1ed1c 1-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn ng\u00e0y 15/6 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. M\u1ed9t m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n l\u00e0 c\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 3-3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 xem l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb v\u00e0 t\u1edbi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn, qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 h\u00e3y theo d\u00f5i clip S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 11 tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean gh\u00e9 th\u0103m v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00e9.</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean <span href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZAiun8-d60VU6Px95pbGPA/videos\" target=\"_blank\">k\u00eanh Youtube c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn</span>:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-10-nhan-dinh-bang-g-421-188564.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 10: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3ng G</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-8-nhan-dinh-bang-f-bang-cua-nha-vua-421-188553.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 8: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3ng F, b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Nh\u00e0 vua</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-7-nhan-dinh-bang-e-421-188456.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 7: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3ng E</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-6-nhan-dinh-bang-d-gap-chua-cuu-the-421-188313.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 6: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3ng D, g\u1eb7p \u201cCh\u00faa c\u1ee9u th\u1ebf\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-4-nhan-dinh-bang-c-ai-ve-ai-tiep-421-188185.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 4: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3ng C \u2013 Ai v\u1ec1, ai ti\u1ebfp?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-2-nhan-dinh-bang-b-de-me-cung-thanh-tho-421-188126.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 2: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3ng B, \u0111\u00ea m\u00ea c\u00f9ng \u201cth\u00e1nh th\u01a1\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nong-bongda24hvn-so-huu-ban-quyen-song-cung-world-cup-2018-421-188075.html\">N\u00d3NG: Bongda24h.vn s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t serie S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBongda24h.vn (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong><br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"224","checkdouble":"188642"},{"date":"15:37 16/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u Argentina vs Iceland","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/ket-qua-bong-da-argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Iceland s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 di\u1ec5n ra c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn trong c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Bongda24h.vn s\u1ebd l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>Argentina vs Iceland<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian: </em>20h ng\u00e0y 16/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>Otkrytiye Arena (th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Moskva)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Argentina -0.93*0:1 1/2*0.88 Iceland<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u 0.91*2 1/2*-0.98 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Argentina vs Iceland\" title=\"Preview Argentina vs Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-argentina-vs-iceland-va-du-doan-argentina-vs-iceland-tren-bongda24h.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Iceland 20h ng\u00e0y 16/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n<strong><br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<strong> </strong><br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i \u1edf Argentina \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, ng\u00f3t ngh\u00e9t m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp m\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i t\u1edbi ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, World Cup 2018 n\u00e0y th\u00f4i, vi\u1ec7c Mauro Icardi, Diego Perotti, Javier Pastore kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn trong ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Argentina. Th\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc khi Manuel Lanzini kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d-463-188637.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d-463-188637.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Argentina vs Iceland 20h00 ng\u00e0y 16/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Argentina vs Iceland: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Argentina v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Lionel Messi \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh anh nh\u01b0 Gonzalo Higuain, Sergio Aguero, Angel Di Maria hay Paulo Dybala c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u00f9 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn Argentina v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi ng\u1edd l\u1edbn. \u0110\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 l\u00fac HLV Jorge Sampaoli \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 cho La Albiceleste \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina\" title=\"Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Carlos-Tevez-phat-bieu-ve-Lionel-Messi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Argentina s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Sampaoli quay l\u1ea1i s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u1ec9 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u00ea th\u1ea3m nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed: 1-6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 3 v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Iceland, ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u Otkrytiye Arena kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Argentina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng, ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn Argentina v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi ng\u1edd l\u1edbn. \u0110\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 l\u00fac HLV Jorge Sampaoli \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 cho La Albiceleste \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Sampaoli quay l\u1ea1i s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u1ec9 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u00ea th\u1ea3m nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed: 1-6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 3 v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Isco tren DT TBN thang Argentina\" title=\"Isco tren DT TBN thang Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/goc-nhin-isco-tren-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Argrentina l\u1ea1i m\u1ecfng manh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Iceland, ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Otkrytiye Arena, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, ngo\u00e0i phong c\u00e1ch, nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Sergio Romero c\u1ee7a Man United r\u00fat lui, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Willy Caballero s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e3 36 tu\u1ed5i, m\u1edbi 6 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tri\u1ec1n mi\u00ean t\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Iceland tai World Cup 2018 la an so thu vi.\" title=\"\u0110T Iceland t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 \u1ea9n s\u1ed1 th\u00fa v\u1ecb.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/8/iceland-9.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Iceland c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c khi 2 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00f4 danh: Nahuel Guzman v\u00e0 Franco Armani v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Caballero c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i cho La Albiceleste m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 50% s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ngh\u0129 theo h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Argentina l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, Nicolas Otamendi l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng tin duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Argentina. D\u00f9 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi sao Man City hay hai c\u00e1nh, d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. Iceland kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t d\u1ecb. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u hay &ldquo;b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft&rdquo; r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t Gylfi Sigurdsson c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t Argentina b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (T\u1eeb 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\n- <strong>Argentina s\u1ebd th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1:<strong> Argentina th\u1eafng 3-1</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 9 qu\u1ea3 (U 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- Th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Iceland. <br>\r\n- Th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Iceland.<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Iceland tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi Argentina (+1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t trong hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm l\u00e0 1 (U 1)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"223","checkdouble":"188644"},{"date":"16:12 16/06","title":"V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018: Li\u1ec7u s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3m m\u00f9a World Cup?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/14/vong-14-vleague-2018-lieu-suc-nong-co-giam-mua-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00f2ng 14 V-League di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u00edt nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m World Cup 2018 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t \u0111i nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tuy nhi\u00ean S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i n\u00ean r\u1eb1ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ngang c\u01a1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn play-off tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng ho\u1eb7c x\u1ea5u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 Khi s\u1ee9c h\u00fat gi\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7t m\u00f9a World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 Khi s\u1ee9c h\u00fat gi\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7t m\u00f9a World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/ha-noi-dai-thang-tai-vleague-da-den-luc-nghi-nghiem-tuc-ve-san-choi-chau-luc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Li\u1ec7u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f3 ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m cho n\u1ed7i lo c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em l\u1edbn h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u2018\u0111\u1ed9c c\u00f4 c\u1ea7u b\u1ea1i\u2019 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c V-League v\u1edbi 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi 13 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea3 n\u1ed9i\u00a0 l\u1eabn ngo\u1ea1i. V\u00ec th\u1ebf s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 14.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u0110V \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o l\u00e0 HAGL \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf Pleiku v\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t penalty tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 2-0 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch. Trong 3 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, HAGL \u0111ang gi\u1eef m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch to\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Than Quang Ninh vs HAGL\" title=\"Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/sep-hagl-khong-hai-long-ve-hieu-suat-thi-dau-cua-cong-phuong-va-cac-dong-doi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>CLB HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c l\u00e0 1-3 v\u00e0 0-1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, HAGL may ra m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00e0 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn 6 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai 17/6. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 7 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00e0 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u nay, 16/6.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t h\u1eb3n l\u00ean nh\u00f3m an to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC 2-1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 9, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u01b0a gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o v\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn thua v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n, s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n, kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu m\u00e0 HLV H\u1ed3ng Vinh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u201cv\u0169 kh\u00ed\u201d c\u1ee7a XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 trong cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda FLC Thanh H\u00f3a, sau\u00a0giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n V-League \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng\u00a0\u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1p 4 \u0111\u00fang 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, n\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t sau v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi Thanh H\u00f3a l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 10 tr\u00ean BXH, HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i. Song li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng?</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"LTD vong 14 V-League 2018\" title=\"LT\u0110 v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Vong-14-V-League-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>LT\u0110 v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\n\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:#3a3a3a;background:#fafafa\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"222","checkdouble":"188647"},{"date":"10:22 16/06","title":"Diego Costa b\u1ee9c x\u00fac khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/diego-costa-buc-xuc-khi-tbn-bi-cam-hoa.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Diego Costa cho r\u1eb1ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn Iberia v\u1eeba qua.</h2><h2>Diego Costa l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, Costa b\u1ee9c x\u00fac h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, Costa b\u1ee9c x\u00fac h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Tay-Ban-Nha-bi-cam-hoa,-Costa-buc-xuc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Costa l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00e3 hai l\u1ea7n gi\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 khi Ronaldo ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Fernando Hierro \u0111\u00e3 trao cho Costa c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay v\u00ec Iago Aspas, Lucas Vazquezhay Rodrigo. V\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf cho Hierro th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e2m mi\u1ec7ng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t sung m\u00e3n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c khi \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Costa kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 ng\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, g\u1eb7p Ma-r\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Kaliningrad v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 4 tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 Diego Costa cho r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ed1t t\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tranh lu\u1eadn. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng may cho Costa l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lu m\u1edd b\u1edfi hat-trick c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. V\u00e0 sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Iran \u0111ang t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng B nh\u1edd chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma-r\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pique-buc-xuc-ronaldo-gioi-an-va-de-kiem-da-phat-421-188609.html\">Pique b\u1ee9c x\u00fac: Ronaldo gi\u1ecfi \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-sieu-kich-tinh-421-188601.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"221","checkdouble":"188614"},{"date":"10:06 16/06","title":"Ronaldo \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n troll \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-an-mung-ban-thang-bang-man-troll-dich-thu-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00eam qua, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ea1y th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u1eb1ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea5y tay vu\u1ed1t c\u1eb1m v\u1edbi d\u1ee5ng \u00fd \"\u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y\" Lionel Messi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huy-diet-tay-ban-nha-ronaldo-lap-them-ky-luc-moi-469-188608.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eeba x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span> sau khi l\u1eadp hat-trick \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Seleccao tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN. CR7 s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo troll Messi khi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u0110N 3-3 TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo troll Messi khi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u0110N 3-3 TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Ronaldo_an_mung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pha \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea7y khi\u00eau kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Messi. \u1ea2nh: Getty Images.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nY\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0103n m\u1eebng sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0a tay l\u00ean c\u1eb1m v\u00e0 chu m\u00f4i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t d\u00e1ng v\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y khi\u00eau kh\u00edch. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia, m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Real Madrid nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ec3 \"\u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y\" ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Lionel Messi, \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 truy\u1ec1n ki\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a anh su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ed9t h\u00e3ng s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1ec3 thao ch\u1ea1y chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina v\u1edbi slogan: \"Leo Messi: The G.O.A.T\". Trong \u0111\u00f3, \"G.O.A.T\" l\u00e0 vi\u1ebft t\u1eaft c\u1ee7a c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb ti\u1ebfng Anh \"Greatest Of All Time\" (t\u1ea1m d\u1ecbch: hay nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i).\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buc anh Messi dang be mot chu de nam trong chien dich quang cao\" title=\"B\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh Messi \u0111ang b\u1ebf m\u1ed9t ch\u00fa d\u00ea n\u1eb1m trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Messi_quang_cao_1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh Messi \u0111ang b\u1ebf m\u1ed9t ch\u00fa d\u00ea n\u1eb1m trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \"Leo Messi: The G.O.A.T\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong ti\u1ebfng Anh, \"goat\" c\u00f2n c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 con d\u00ea. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Ronaldo d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng gi\u1ea3 con v\u1eadt n\u00e0y trong pha \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u1eb1m g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch: T\u00f4i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 G.O.A.T ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi, li\u1ec7u Messi c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi? 20h t\u1ed1i nay 16/6, Messi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Iceland, \"ng\u1ef1a \u00f4\" t\u1ea1i EURO 2016 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>.<br>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"220","checkdouble":"188615"},{"date":"10:28 16/06","title":"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 16/6","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/lich-truyen-hinh-truc-tiep-world-cup-2018-hom-nay-166.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang b\u00e1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 16/6 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i VTV v\u00e0 HTV v\u00e0 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng internet</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 166 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 166 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/lich-truyen-hinh-truc-tiep-world-cup-2018-hom-nay-16-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo g\u1ecdi Messi li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\nLo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n v\u1edbi 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i nay v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai thu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3ng C v\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng D. \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u1eeb Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 Australia. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n theo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Australia c\u1ee7a bongda24h \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng 3-0.  <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D Argentina s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0110T Iceland t\u1eebng g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i Euro 2016. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D Croatia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh Nigeria<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich truyen hinh truc tiep World Cup 2018 dem nay 16/6\" title=\"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay 16/6\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/lich-truyen-hinh-truc-tiep-world-cup-2018-dem-nay-16-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>+ <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-australia-17h00-ngay-166-dau-xuoi-duoi-lot-421-188596.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Australia b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Australia b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div>+ <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-argentina-vs-iceland-20h00-ngay-166-giai-ma-hien-tuong-421-188591.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div>+ <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-peru-vs-dan-mach-23h-ngay-166-khac-biet-o-eriksen-462-188607.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div>+ <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-nigeria-02h00-ngay-176-ban-ha-dai-bang-421-188592.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"219","checkdouble":"188616"},{"date":"10:59 16/06","title":"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ba b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng Sochi, Cristiano Ronaldo thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp c\u00fa hat-trick th\u1ee9 51, trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed 88 n\u0103m c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p 16 n\u0103m qu\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f9i \u00e1o s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadt tr\u1edb tr\u00eau, ch\u01b0a n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng sau khi khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u0103m th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, gi\u1edd th\u00ec Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp mang \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i \u0111au cho ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">48 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/tbn-mat-dau-truoc-world-cup-2018-tia-sang-hy-vong-nao-le-loi-giua-chon-hon-mang-loan-lac-421-188570.html\" target=\"_blank\">La Roja &ldquo;m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7u&rdquo; ngay th\u1ec1m khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018</span> v\u1edbi tr\u00e1t sa th\u1ea3i s\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u00e0nh cho Julen Lopetegui, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00ecn gi\u1eef th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam minh trong l\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 sau khi HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 ngang nhi\u00ean \u0111i \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB tr\u1ef1c thu\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Ronaldo-o-tran-Bo-Dao-Nha-3-3-Tay-Ban-Nha-Hat-trick-ruc-ro!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hat-trick r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Bernabeu v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua &ldquo;gi\u00fap&rdquo; Real Madrid ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c bao ph\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111en l\u00ean chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1ed1n r\u1ea5t chi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai ph\u00fat v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n n\u1eefa th\u00f4i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ng\u1ee1 r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng, l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ngay trong th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc r\u1ed1i ren, lo\u1ea1n l\u1ea1c. Nacho c\u0169ng v\u1eady, v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n &ldquo;t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng&rdquo; n\u00e0o ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n d\u00e0nh cho anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00fat 4, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i&hellip; kh\u00f4ng, anh ng\u00e2y th\u01a1 b\u1ecb Ronaldo qua m\u1eb7t trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, chi\u1ebfu theo n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi tinh qu\u00e1i, &ldquo;\u0111\u1ec3u&rdquo; c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea5p CLB sau khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m penalty.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00fat 58, ch\u00ednh anh v\u1edbi c\u00fa vu\u1ed1t b\u00f3ng m\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i s\u1ea5m s\u00e9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-2 v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec \u01b0u th\u1ebf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 trong n\u1eeda gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 ti\u1ebfp theo, cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p CR7 l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi c\u00fa hat-trick th\u1ee9 51, trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed 88 n\u0103m c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p 16 n\u0103m qu\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f9i \u00e1o s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Bo-Dao-Nha-3-3-Tay-Ban-Nha-Chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh,-Cristiano-Ronaldo!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hat-trick r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0? Ronaldo ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i Ronaldo, m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u00edch k\u1ef7 v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00e1u b\u1eb3n v\u00e0 b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c khi m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n? Th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng b\u1ecf ngo\u00e0i tai. \u0110\u00eam Sochi \u0111\u00e3 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho ni\u1ec1m tin \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00f2n m\u1ecfi c\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 mang vinh quang v\u1ec1 cho T\u1ed5 qu\u1ed1c. Sau khi s\u1edbm chia tay tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Euro 2016 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n cho anh n\u1ebfu l\u1ee7i th\u1ee7i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft t\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfi l\u0103n d\u00e0i tr\u00ean m\u00e1 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m c\u00e1i \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ai c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho anh. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u si\u00eau sao Man Utd thay \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Fernando Santos l\u00e0m lu\u00f4n HLV ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, th\u1ed1ng l\u0129nh khu v\u1ef1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi anh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Bo-Dao-Nha-3-3-Tay-Ban-Nha-Chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh,-Cristiano-Ronaldo!-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hat-trick r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1eeb Paris \u0111\u1ebfn Sochi, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n Ronaldo n\u1ebfu anh bu\u00f4ng b\u1ecf sau tuy\u1ec7t ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Nacho, hay sau khi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng &ndash; m\u1ed9t penalty v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e0 bi\u1ebfu t\u1eeb David De Gea &ndash; \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a b\u1edfi c\u00f4ng lao t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Diego Costa. N\u00f3i th\u1eb3ng ra, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n mang ngh\u0129a l\u00fd g\u00ec s\u1ea5t n\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1eabn mang trong m\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng mi\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Ronaldo bi\u1ebfn t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn th\u00e0nh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t Ronaldo d\u1ed7i h\u1eddn, c\u00e1u b\u1eb3n hay v\u00f9ng v\u1eb1ng trong b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi CR7 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd thu\u1eadn theo t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-sieu-kich-tinh-421-188601.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/diem-nhan-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-sieu-kich-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-sieu-kich-tinh-421-188601.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span><br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean Ronaldo v\u00e0 De Gea. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn derby b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea3n l\u0129nh gi\u00fap anh m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m ng\u00fat ng\u00e0n \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh g\u00ec ph\u00fat 90 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 \u00edt gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4i, anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3ng ph\u1ea1t 18,8 tri\u1ec7u Euro k\u00e8m hai n\u0103m t\u00f9 treo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadn hi\u1ebfn v\u00ec T\u1ed5 qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn v\u1eb9n nguy\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat suy chuy\u1ec3n hay sao nh\u00e3ng, v\u00e0 th\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c th\u00f4ng qua sai l\u1ea7m s\u01a1 \u0111\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n hi\u1ebfm hoi c\u1ee7a De Gea, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hat-trick r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i khi m\u1ecdi hy v\u1ecdng t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea1n ki\u1ec7t, khi m\u1ecdi trang nh\u1ea5t m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 vua Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 n\u00e1t b\u01b0\u01a1m t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong, Ronaldo m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fd mu\u00f4n thu\u1edf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i ph\u00ed ph\u1ea1m m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh ngon \u0103n nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi khi? Ronaldo s\u1ebd s\u00fat tr\u00fang h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o? Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t ghi b\u00e0n n\u1eefa? Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00f4m nay, v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ecbch s\u1eed trong c\u00e1i ch\u00f4n ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a De Gea c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ebft l\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft&hellip;. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo; &ndash; Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sergio Ramos tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-463-188575.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span>&nbsp;k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Ronaldo. Anh \u0111\u00e3 sai, qu\u00e1 sai v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u1ea1nh b\u00ean \u1edf Real Madrid r\u1ed3i!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so Bo Dao Nha 3-3 Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Thong-so-BDN.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha-421-188598.html\">Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huy-diet-tay-ban-nha-ronaldo-lap-them-ky-luc-moi-469-188608.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Ronaldo l\u1eadp h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-an-mung-ban-thang-bang-man-troll-dich-thu-messi-421-188615.html\">Ronaldo \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n troll \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/lap-hattrick-ronaldo-duoc-dong-doi-ca-ngoi-het-loi-469-188611.html\">Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi sau c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-mot-minh-ronaldo-nhay-mua-giua-dan-bo-tot-421-188600.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Ronaldo nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00e0n B\u00f2 t\u00f3t</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"218","checkdouble":"188617"},{"date":"10:47 16/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 16/6: L\u1eadp hattrick, Ronaldo tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/16/tin-nong-world-cup-2018-ngay-166-lap-hattrick-ronaldo-tren-dinh-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (16/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1eadp hattrick, Ronaldo tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">V\u1edbi hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi De Gea, Ronaldo x\u1ebfp ngang h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Pele, Klose v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n trong 4 m\u00f9a World Cup, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi CR7 c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 ph\u00e1 \"k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c\" c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 166 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 166 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Ronaldo-o-tran-Bo-Dao-Nha-3-3-Tay-Ban-Nha-Hat-trick-ruc-ro!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHat-trick c\u1ee7a Ronaldo gi\u00fap anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ea7y vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 4 ghi b\u00e0n trong 4 m\u00f9a World Cup tham d\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Pele v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Uwe Seeler c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 1958, 1962, 1966 v\u00e0 1970. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n trong su\u1ed1t 4 m\u00f9a l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 World Cup Miroslav Klose (2002, 2006, 2010 v\u00e0 n\u0103m 2014).</div>\r\n<h2>Gerard Pique: 'Ronaldo hay \u0103n v\u1ea1 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t'</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique c\u1ee7a Barcelona nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0: \"T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n, c\u00f2n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u00ec c\u00f3 3 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ghi 3 b\u00e0n\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Ph\u1ea3i v\u1ef1c d\u1eady trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup khi ch\u1ecbu m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra\", Pique chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 3 c\u1ee7a \"La Roja\" c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Ronaldo ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn: \"Cristiano r\u1ea5t hay \u0103n v\u1ea1\". B\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha - qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n 11 m - xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ng\u00e3 r\u1ea5t k\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. <br>\r\n<em>Tin b\u00e0i chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pique-buc-xuc-ronaldo-gioi-an-va-de-kiem-da-phat-421-188609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/pique-buc-xuc-ronaldo-gioi-an-va-de-kiem-da-phat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pique-buc-xuc-ronaldo-gioi-an-va-de-kiem-da-phat-421-188609.html\">Pique b\u1ee9c x\u00fac: Ronaldo gi\u1ecfi \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t</span><br>\r\n<span>Trung v\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ee9c x\u00fac sau khi Cristiano Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick, gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>M\u00e8o \u201cti\u00ean tri\u201d Achilles d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 100%</h2>\r\n<div>Sau khi \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00fang k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Nga - \u1ea2 R\u1eadp, ch\u00fa m\u00e8o khi\u1ebfm th\u00ednh Achilles ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y s\u1ed1t khi ch\u1ecdn Iran th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Maroc. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u00e9p s\u00e2n trong su\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Bouhaddouz \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u201cs\u01b0 t\u1eed\u201d ch\u00e2u Phi \u00f4m h\u1eadn. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, m\u00e8o Achilles v\u1eabn \u0111ang xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u00fang 100% k\u00e8o World Cup 2018.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thanh-meo-achilles-lai-du-doan-chinh-xac-ket-qua-world-cup-2018-421-188602.html\">Th\u00e1nh m\u00e8o Achilles l\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1eb7t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u1edf Nga khi\u1ebfn HLV Joachim Low lo l\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div>C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh \u1edf v\u00f9ng ngo\u1ea1i \u00f4 th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Moscow l\u00e0 Vatutinki v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a CLB CSKA Moscow. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Joachim Low \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. \"\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng ng\u1ecdn c\u1ecf t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y qu\u00e1 d\u00e0i. T\u00f4i mong r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c ngay ng\u00e0y mai\".</div>\r\n<h2>Griezmann s\u1ebd nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n n\u1eefa</h2>\r\n<div>HLV \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, Didier Deschamps kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f2n nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u201cL\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e2m l\u00fd khi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Griezmann t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Khi g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd b\u1ecb c\u1edfi b\u1ecf, Griezmann s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Griezmann s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar dung thu ba trong danh sach ghi ban cua DT Brazil.\" title=\"Neymar \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba trong danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/neymar-vi-da-voi-ao-nhu-di-danh-nhau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Neymar t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div>Tr\u00ean k\u00eanh Youtube c\u1ee7a Brazil, Desimpedidos, Neymar t\u1ef1 tin anh ch\u1ec9 thua k\u00e9m Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi: \u201cHai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi. V\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 khi\u00eam nh\u01b0\u1eddng, gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u1edfi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb h\u00e0nh tinh kh\u00e1c\u201d.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"217","checkdouble":"188618"}]}